{#-
  DataTable — the kit's fully-featured workhorse compound for tabular data.

  Composes the 4 S2.4a tables foundations (Table + Pagination + ScrollArea +
  Resizable — the last two are consumer's opt-in wrap) + 4 selection primitives
  (Checkbox bare-mode for select-all header + row checkboxes ; DropdownMenu
  for column-visibility ; AlertDialog for bulk-destructive — wired by the
  consumer via the dispatched `data-table:bulk-action` event).

  Per OQ-34 (vanilla — sealed S2.4 opening), OQ-37 (single-col sort default,
  opt-in multi-col), OQ-38 (text Input filter default), OQ-39 (AlertDialog
  for bulk-destructive ; Sonner Toast-with-Undo deferred to S2.5+).

  Composes:
    - 1 Stimulus controller `data-table` (orchestrates sort + selection +
      column-visibility + bulk + filter — see data-table_controller.js).
    - [Table](../table/) primitive — `.cremona-table` classes verbatim + the
      block-override hook (we render our own <thead> + <tbody> inside).
    - [Pagination](../pagination/) compound — footer with inline page-size.
    - [Checkbox](../checkbox/) primitive — bare-mode for select-all header
      + per-row checkboxes (S1.3 indeterminate doctrine via
      `el.indeterminate = true`, browser-managed aria-checked="mixed").
    - [Empty](../empty/) primitive — empty-state row when rows array is
      empty (composed via `<tr><td colspan="N">`).
    - [Icon](../icon/) primitive (curated 30 set) — settings, trash-2, etc.

  Per WAI-ARIA APG: native `<table>` semantic (NOT `role="grid"` — see
  DataTable.md §7 doctrine). aria-sort on sortable headers, aria-selected
  on selected rows, aria-checked="mixed" auto-emitted by the browser when
  el.indeterminate is true (S1.3 doctrine — NEVER stamp manually).

  Parameters:
    htmlId                (string,  optional) — auto-generated.
    caption               (string,  optional) — accessible caption.
    captionSrOnly         (bool,    optional) — true → caption visually hidden
                                                but announced.
    size                  (string,  optional) — sm | md (default) | lg.
                                                Forwarded to Table.
    variant               (string,  optional) — default | striped. Forwarded.
    columns               (array,   required) — column definitions.
      Each: { id, label, sortable?, sortDir?, filterType?, filterValue?,
             filterPlaceholder?, align?, numeric?, visible?, togglable? }
    rows                  (array,   required) — row data.
      Each: { id, cells: [{ content, numeric?, align? }, …], selected? }
    page                  (int,     optional) — initial pagination page.
    pageSize              (int,     optional) — initial rows per page.
    totalRows             (int,     optional) — total across pages.
    pageSizes             (array,   optional) — [10, 25, 50, 100].
    paginationLabels      (array,   optional) — { label, pageSizeLabel,
                                                  firstAriaLabel, … } for
                                                  the Pagination compound.
    selectable            (bool,    optional) — default true. Adds select-all
                                                + per-row checkboxes.
    selectedRows          (array,   optional) — SSR pre-selection (row.id).
    multiColumnSort       (bool,    optional) — default false. OQ-37 opt-in.
    showColumnVisibility  (bool,    optional) — default true.
    columnVisibilityLabel (string,  optional) — default 'Colonnes'.
    bulkActions           (array,   optional) — toolbar bulk-action buttons.
      Each: { id, label, variant?, iconLeading?, destructive? }
    emptyTitle            (string,  optional) — empty-row title.
    emptyBody             (string,  optional) — empty-row body.
    emptyCta              (string,  optional) — empty-row CTA label (secondary).
    emptyCtaAction        (string,  optional) — Stimulus action descriptor
                                                fired on emptyCta click (e.g.
                                                "click->myConsumer#clearFilters").

  Blocks:
    toolbar — extra toolbar content (e.g. a "Nouveau" primary button).
    empty   — full Empty primitive composition (overrides emptyTitle/Body/Cta).

  Events emitted (raw CustomEvent on the wrap):
    data-table:sort-change       — detail.{column, direction, isMultiCol}
    data-table:selection-change  — detail.{selectedRows, count}
    data-table:column-visibility-change — detail.{visibleColumns}
    data-table:bulk-action       — detail.{actionId, selectedRows}
    data-table:filter-change     — detail.{column, query, allFilters}

  Bubbled from nested compounds:
    pagination:change            — detail.{page, pageSize, from, to, total,
                                           totalPages}
    popover:open / popover:close — from the column-visibility DropdownMenu
-#}

{%- set htmlId               = htmlId               | default('cremona-data-table-' ~ random()) -%}
{%- set caption              = caption              | default(null) -%}
{%- set captionSrOnly        = captionSrOnly        | default(true) -%}
{%- set size                 = size                 | default('md') -%}
{%- set variant              = variant              | default('default') -%}
{%- set columns              = columns              | default([]) -%}
{%- set rows                 = rows                 | default([]) -%}
{%- set page                 = page                 | default(1) -%}
{%- set pageSize             = pageSize             | default(25) -%}
{%- set totalRows            = totalRows            | default(rows | length) -%}
{%- set pageSizes            = pageSizes            | default([10, 25, 50, 100]) -%}
{%- set paginationLabels     = paginationLabels     | default({}) -%}
{%- set selectable           = selectable           | default(true) -%}
{%- set selectedRows         = selectedRows         | default([]) -%}
{%- set multiColumnSort      = multiColumnSort      | default(false) -%}
{%- set showColumnVisibility = showColumnVisibility | default(true) -%}
{%- set columnVisibilityLabel = columnVisibilityLabel | default('Colonnes') -%}
{%- set columnVisibilityAria = columnVisibilityAria | default('Afficher / masquer les colonnes') -%}
{%- set bulkActions          = bulkActions          | default([]) -%}
{%- set emptyTitle           = emptyTitle           | default('Aucun résultat') -%}
{%- set emptyBody            = emptyBody            | default('Aucun élément ne correspond aux filtres.') -%}
{%- set emptyCta             = emptyCta             | default(null) -%}
{%- set emptyCtaAction       = emptyCtaAction       | default(null) -%}
{%- set ariaSelectAll        = ariaSelectAll        | default('Tout sélectionner') -%}
{%- set ariaDeselect         = ariaDeselect         | default('Désélectionner') -%}
{%- set ariaSelectRow        = ariaSelectRow        | default('Sélectionner la ligne') -%}
{%- set ariaFilter           = ariaFilter           | default('Filtrer') -%}
{%- set className            = className            | default('') -%}
{# controllerExtras (array, optional, default []) — additional Stimulus controllers
   to compose on the same wrap element (e.g. ['sortable'] for sortable rows).
   Per ADR-0048 Ring 2 amend ; consumer MUST NOT include 'data-table' (auto-injected). #}
{%- set controllerExtras     = controllerExtras     | default([]) -%}

{# Build the list of all visible column ids — used for the initial visibleColumns value. #}
{%- set _visibleIds = [] -%}
{%- for col in columns -%}
  {%- if col.visible | default(true) -%}
    {%- set _visibleIds = _visibleIds | merge([col.id]) -%}
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}

{# Build the total column count for empty-row colspan (visible cols + select cell if selectable). #}
{%- set _colspanTotal = _visibleIds | length + (selectable ? 1 : 0) -%}

{# Does any column have a filter? Drives the conditional filter row render. #}
{%- set _hasAnyFilter = false -%}
{%- for col in columns -%}
  {%- if col.filterType is defined and col.filterType -%}
    {%- set _hasAnyFilter = true -%}
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}

{%- set _classes = ['cremona-data-table'] -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

<div
  id="{{ htmlId }}"
  class="{{ _classes | join(' ') }}"
  data-controller="{{ (['data-table'] | merge(controllerExtras)) | join(' ') }}"
  data-action="click->data-table#toggleSort change->data-table#toggleRow change->data-table#toggleSelectAll change->data-table#toggleColumnVisibility input->data-table#filter click->data-table#bulkAction click->data-table#clearSelection"
  data-data-table-sort-column-value=""
  data-data-table-sort-dir-value="none"
  data-data-table-selected-rows-value="{{ selectedRows | json_encode }}"
  data-data-table-visible-columns-value="{{ _visibleIds | json_encode }}"
  data-data-table-total-rows-value="{{ totalRows }}"
  data-data-table-multi-column-sort-value="{{ multiColumnSort ? 'true' : 'false' }}"
>

  {# ---- Toolbar (bulk-bar + column-vis) ---- #}
  {%- if selectable or bulkActions | length > 0 or showColumnVisibility -%}
    <div class="cremona-data-table__toolbar">

      {%- if selectable or bulkActions | length > 0 -%}
        <div
          class="cremona-data-table__bulk-bar"
          data-data-table-target="bulkBar"
          hidden
        >
          <span
            class="cremona-data-table__bulk-count"
            data-data-table-target="bulkCount"
            aria-live="polite"
            aria-atomic="true"
          ></span>
          <div class="cremona-data-table__bulk-actions" role="group">
            {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
              label: ariaDeselect,
              variant: 'ghost',
              size: 'sm',
              attrs: { 'data-action': 'click->data-table#clearSelection' },
            } only %}
            {%- for action in bulkActions -%}
              {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
                label: action.label,
                variant: action.variant | default('secondary'),
                size: 'sm',
                iconLeading: action.iconLeading | default(null),
                attrs: { 'data-bulk-action-id': action.id, 'data-action': 'click->data-table#bulkAction' },
              } only %}
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if showColumnVisibility -%}
        <div
          class="cremona-data-table__column-visibility"
          data-data-table-target="columnVisibilityTrigger"
        >
          {% embed '@cremona/components/dropdown-menu/dropdown-menu.html.twig' with {
            htmlId: htmlId ~ '-col-vis',
            placement: 'bottom-end',
            offset: 4,
            closeOnItemClick: false,
            className: 'cremona-data-table__column-visibility-menu',
          } %}
            {% block trigger %}
              {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
                label: columnVisibilityLabel,
                variant: 'secondary',
                size: 'sm',
                iconLeading: 'settings',
                attrs: {
                  'data-popover-target': 'trigger',
                  'aria-haspopup': 'menu',
                  'aria-expanded': 'false',
                  'aria-controls': popoverHtmlId,
                  'aria-label': columnVisibilityAria,
                },
              } only %}
            {% endblock %}
            {% block items %}
              {%- for col in columns -%}
                {%- if col.togglable | default(true) -%}
                  {% embed '@cremona/components/item/item.html.twig' with { attrs: { role: 'menuitem' } } %}
                    {% block content %}
                      <label class="cremona-data-table__column-visibility-option">
                        <input
                          type="checkbox"
                          class="cremona-checkbox__input"
                          data-data-table-column-vis="{{ col.id }}"
                          data-action="change->data-table#toggleColumnVisibility"
                          {%- if col.visible | default(true) %} checked{% endif -%}
                        >
                        <span>{{ col.label }}</span>
                      </label>
                    {% endblock %}
                  {% endembed %}
                {%- endif -%}
              {%- endfor -%}
            {% endblock %}
          {% endembed %}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {# ---- Table — composes the Table primitive via the block override path. ---- #}
  {% embed '@cremona/components/table/table.html.twig' with {
    htmlId: htmlId ~ '-table',
    caption: caption,
    captionSrOnly: captionSrOnly,
    size: size,
    variant: variant,
    className: 'cremona-data-table__table',
  } %}
    {% block thead %}
      <thead class="cremona-table__thead" data-data-table-target="table-thead">
        <tr>
          {% if selectable %}
            <th class="cremona-data-table__select-all-cell">
              {% include '@cremona/components/checkbox/checkbox.html.twig' with {
                size: 'sm',
                ariaLabel: ariaSelectAll,
                attrs: {
                  'data-data-table-target': 'selectAllCheckbox',
                  'data-action': 'change->data-table#toggleSelectAll',
                },
              } only %}
            </th>
          {% endif %}
          {% for col in columns %}
            {%- set colSortable = col.sortable | default(false) -%}
            {%- set colSortDir = col.sortDir | default('none') -%}
            {%- set colAlign = col.numeric | default(false) ? 'end' : (col.align | default(null)) -%}
            {%- set colNumeric = col.numeric | default(false) -%}
            {%- set colVisible = col.visible | default(true) -%}
            <th
              data-data-table-column="{{ col.id }}"
              data-data-table-column-cell="{{ col.id }}"
              {%- if colAlign %} data-align="{{ colAlign }}"{% endif -%}
              {%- if colNumeric %} data-numeric="true"{% endif -%}
              {%- if colSortable %} data-sortable="true" aria-sort="{{ colSortDir }}"{% endif -%}
              {%- if not colVisible %} hidden{% endif -%}
            >
              {%- if colSortable -%}
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="cremona-table__sort"
                  data-data-table-column="{{ col.id }}"
                  data-sort-dir="{{ colSortDir }}"
                >
                  <span class="cremona-table__sort-label">{{ col.label }}</span>
                  <span class="cremona-table__sort-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
              {%- else -%}
                {{ col.label }}
              {%- endif -%}
            </th>
          {% endfor %}
        </tr>

        {% if _hasAnyFilter %}
          <tr class="cremona-data-table__filter-row" data-data-table-target="filterRow">
            {% if selectable %}<th></th>{% endif %}
            {% for col in columns %}
              {%- set colVisible = col.visible | default(true) -%}
              <th
                data-data-table-column-cell="{{ col.id }}"
                {%- if not colVisible %} hidden{% endif -%}
              >
                {%- if col.filterType is defined and col.filterType -%}
                  {%- if col.filterType != 'text' -%}
                    {# OQ-38: combobox/date filterType warn-fallback to text in S2.4b #}
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {% include '@cremona/components/input/input.html.twig' with {
                    type: 'text',
                    size: 'sm',
                    value: col.filterValue | default(''),
                    placeholder: col.filterPlaceholder | default(ariaFilter),
                    className: 'cremona-data-table__filter-input',
                    attrs: {
                      'data-data-table-filter-column': col.id,
                      'data-action': 'input->data-table#filter',
                      'aria-label': col.label,
                    },
                  } only %}
                {%- endif -%}
              </th>
            {% endfor %}
          </tr>
        {% endif %}
      </thead>
    {% endblock %}

    {% block tbody %}
      <tbody class="cremona-table__tbody">
        {%- if rows | length > 0 -%}
          {%- for row in rows -%}
            {%- set rowSelected = row.selected | default(false) or row.id in selectedRows -%}
            <tr
              data-data-table-row-id="{{ row.id }}"
              {%- if rowSelected %} data-selected="true" aria-selected="true"{% endif -%}
            >
              {%- if selectable -%}
                <td class="cremona-data-table__select-cell">
                  {% include '@cremona/components/checkbox/checkbox.html.twig' with {
                    size: 'sm',
                    checked: rowSelected,
                    ariaLabel: ariaSelectRow ~ ' ' ~ row.id,
                    attrs: {
                      'data-data-table-target': 'rowCheckbox',
                      'data-data-table-row-id': row.id,
                      'data-action': 'change->data-table#toggleRow',
                    },
                  } only %}
                </td>
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- for i, cell in row.cells -%}
                {%- set col = columns[i] | default(null) -%}
                {%- if col is not null -%}
                  {%- set cellAlign = cell.numeric | default(false) ? 'end' : (cell.align | default(col.align | default(null))) -%}
                  {%- set cellNumeric = cell.numeric | default(col.numeric | default(false)) -%}
                  {%- set colVisible = col.visible | default(true) -%}
                  <td
                    data-data-table-column-cell="{{ col.id }}"
                    {%- if cellAlign %} data-align="{{ cellAlign }}"{% endif -%}
                    {%- if cellNumeric %} data-numeric="true"{% endif -%}
                    {%- if not colVisible %} hidden{% endif -%}
                  >{{- cell.content | raw -}}</td>
                {%- endif -%}
              {%- endfor -%}
            </tr>
          {%- endfor -%}
        {%- else -%}
          {# Empty state row — colspan total = visible cols + (selectable ? 1 : 0) #}
          <tr
            class="cremona-data-table__empty-row"
            data-data-table-target="emptyState"
          >
            <td colspan="{{ _colspanTotal }}">
              {% include '@cremona/components/empty/empty.html.twig' with {
                size: 'sm',
                titleLevel: 'h3',
                title: emptyTitle,
                body: emptyBody,
                icon: 'search',
              } only %}
              {%- if emptyCta and emptyCtaAction -%}
                <div class="cremona-data-table__empty-cta">
                  {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
                    label: emptyCta,
                    variant: 'secondary',
                    size: 'sm',
                    attrs: { 'data-action': emptyCtaAction },
                  } only %}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </td>
          </tr>
        {%- endif -%}
      </tbody>
    {% endblock %}
  {% endembed %}

  {# ---- Pagination footer — only when totalRows > pageSize. ---- #}
  {%- if totalRows > pageSize -%}
    <div class="cremona-data-table__pagination-wrap" data-data-table-target="paginationMount">
      {% include '@cremona/components/pagination/pagination.html.twig' with {
        htmlId: htmlId ~ '-pagination',
        page: page,
        pageSize: pageSize,
        totalItems: totalRows,
        pageSizes: pageSizes,
        label: paginationLabels.label | default('Pagination'),
        pageSizeLabel: paginationLabels.pageSizeLabel | default('Lignes par page'),
        firstAriaLabel: paginationLabels.firstAriaLabel | default('Première page'),
        prevAriaLabel: paginationLabels.prevAriaLabel | default('Page précédente'),
        nextAriaLabel: paginationLabels.nextAriaLabel | default('Page suivante'),
        lastAriaLabel: paginationLabels.lastAriaLabel | default('Dernière page'),
      } only %}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

</div>
